# Dataset Plan

## Study Area
Nagpur, India

## Primary Target
Land Surface Temperature (LST)

## Version 1 Features
- NDVI
- NDBI
- Land cover
- Elevation
- Water presence / water mask

## Candidate Data Sources
- Landsat 8/9
- Sentinel-2
- SRTM DEM
- Land cover dataset
- Water mask source

## Initial Time Window
Summer / high-heat period with manageable cloud cover

## Modeling Unit
Raster pixels or sampled grid cells

## Open Questions
- Which exact date range should be used?
- How will LST be derived or sourced?
- Which land cover product is best for the study area?
- Should water be represented as a binary mask or distance-to-water feature?
- What spatial resolution will be used for the final modeling table?
